    """Select a tip key using ``self.tip_weights`` to bias the draw.

    Nonpositive or missing weights are treated as 0. If every weight
    ends up 0 (or ``tip_weights`` is empty), falls back to a uniform
    draw over ``TIPS`` via ``self.rng.choice``.
    """
